dc_description_s: Map shows built-up areas, facilities of interest, cemeteries, boundaries, trigonometrical stations, and vegetation. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes index to adjoining sheets, feet to meters conversion table, and area map of administrative boundaries. "Sheet: Montego Bay. Parts of sheets 31, 41, 32 & 42." "The underwater features depicted on this map should not be relied upon for the purposes of marine navigation." "10/71/5396/OS."
dc_creator_sm: United Kingdom. Overseas Development Administration (Directorate of Overseas Surveys)
dc_publisher_s: Tolworth, England : Directorate of Overseas Surveys, 1971.
